Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.19,0:27:04.34,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be3}Red butterflies with forks and knives ,who like to make a meal of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.93,0:27:15.17,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be3}Life is clockwork quick lightning slow faster on your toes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.87,0:27:27.26,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be3}So eat your sugared dream and face the day before it runs away.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.50,0:26:53.22,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be3}從樹上嗡嗡叫的蜂巢看到小蜜蜂和一陣陣氣流
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.19,0:27:04.34,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be3}紅色的蝴蝶拿著刀叉好像在吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.93,0:27:15.17,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be3}生活就像鬧鐘一樣在你舌尖流失
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.87,0:27:27.26,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\be3}在他溜走之前 那就品嘗著你美味的夢面對著那一天
Comment: 0,0:04:42.78,0:04:42.78,Comment,,0,0,0,,——Text——
